cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with improving text proposals in scene images using convolutional neural networks. 
2. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a likely category as the paper deals with text recognition in images, which is a common task in information retrieval. 
3. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is another possible category as the paper deals with text recognition, which is a natural language processing task. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses machine learning techniques to improve the performance of text proposals. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with text recognition in multimedia (image) data.
